==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: gaga
<hw>gaga</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>mentally or physically
infirm with age.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> doddering, senile.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>marked by foolish or unreasoning fondness; <as>as,
<ex>gaga</ex> over his girlfriend</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> crazy about, dotty, enamored, infatuated, in love,
smitten, soft on(predicate), taken with(predicate).</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gagate</ent>⟦br⟧
